description: BMO Equal Weight Global Base Metals Hedged to CAD Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Solactive Equal Weight Global Base Metals Index Canadian Dollar Hedged, net of expenses. The Fund invests in and holds the Constituent Securities of the Index in the same proportion as they are reflected in the Index. The Fund invests in and holds Canadian and US securities and ADRs. U.S. dollar currency exposure is hedged back to Canadian dollars.
name: BMO Equal Weight Global Base Metals Hedged to CAD Index ETF
